@import Main._

@p
  Bucky is a library which helps Scala programs interact with @lnk("AMQP", "https://www.amqp.org/about/what") message brokers such as @lnk("RabbitMQ", "https://www.rabbitmq.com/").

@p
  It gives an idiomatic Scala interface for:
@ul
  @li
    Publishing to exchanges
  @li
    Consuming from queues
  @li
    Declaring resources
  @li
    Patterns combining all of the above
